  {
    "name": "Color swatches",
    "settings": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "Add swatch image files to your store's [files area](/admin/settings/files). Make sure the file names match the names of your color variants, replacing spaces and special characters with hyphens. For example, a variant called Burly Wood would need a file named 'burly-wood.png'."
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": "[Learn more about color swatches.](https://documentation.fuelthemes.net/kb/how-do-i-set-up-product-variant-swatches/)"
